---
title: Maple-Glazed Pork Chops with Garlic-Butter Corn and Kale Slaw
description: Maple glazed pork chops aren't the only star in this dish. We've upgraded the corn with homemade garlic butter. Don't forget about crunchy kale slaw. Sure to be a summer favourite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-de-porc-glacees-a-lerable-afc31c4a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/maple-glazed-pork-chops-5b25381d30006c1f0c771382-1c50ad64.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/maple-glazed-pork-chops-5b25381d30006c1f0c771382
